Managed Services Manager
Bangalore, Hyderabad, India
Ref#: 144595
Provide leadership for technical team within ITO-I services teams. The team is responsible for applications running on ITO-I owned infrastructure supporting LCM teams and enablement teams within AT&T. While the candidate will need some technical knowledge to communicate with the team and with IT Development and others, this is a team leader role and requires good people skills, task and resource management, flexibility in working hours and able to communicate well through voice and presentations, and a willingness to continually improve the way we work using automation and process improvements to drive improvements. The candidate will be working with other team leaders within the organization and supported to deliver the best support to enable the applications to be available for their user community.
Kindly note : The successful candidate will have to work with people from all over the globe.
